      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Which brands do you install?</strong><br />Tesla Wall Connector, ChargePoint Home Flex, Wallbox Pulsar
        Plus, Grizzl-E, Emporia, and any UL-listed Level 2 unit. Hardwired or NEMA 14-50 outlet, your call.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Are there Michigan rebates for installing an EV charger?</strong><br />Yes. Consumers Energy's
